H0.text: What is an alternative name for vitamin B9, essential in promoting cell growth, particularly during pregnancy. Folicin

H1.text: What is an alternative name for vitamin B9, essential in promoting cell growth, particularly during pregnancy. Vitabine

H2.text: What is an alternative name for vitamin B9, essential in promoting cell growth, particularly during pregnancy. Folate

H3.text: What is an alternative name for vitamin B9, essential in promoting cell growth, particularly during pregnancy. Folbal

A4.text: Folate is also known as vitamin B9 and folacin, is one of the B vitamins.

A5.text: Folate is required for the body to make DNA and RNA and metabolise amino acids necessary for cell division and maturation of blood cells.
